      "text": "Legende\n\n🟦 LLM-Call (DGX)\n🟩 SQL/Read (Supabase)\n🟪 Web (Tavily)\n🟥 Data-Ingestion\n\n———\n\nKey Metrics:\n• 100% Pass-Rate (20/20)\n• Schnitt 45s/Frage\n• DB-Only: ~30s\n• Multi-Hop: ~70s\n• 0 € laufende Kosten",
